title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H2 - Sep 10 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H2 - Sep 10 2022
description:
The latest FBI leak to the Washington Post on supposed nuclear "secrets" found in the documents seized at Mar-a-Lago shows you just how desperate the Deep State is to get Trump. C&B take a call from the grandfather of a Duke lacrosse player on the latest Duke hoax allegations. Cameron Sexton, Tennessee Speaker of the House, joins Clay and Buck with details on the senseless (and preventable) Eliza Fletcher murder. USA Today smears Clay as a "right-wing extremist" for daring to question the Duke-BYU volleyball story. A former BYU women's basketball player calls in to discuss the story.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
